description:
Choppa Zoe star of Money & Violence sits down with the ladies of Lip Service to discuss being catfished, lasting long in the bedroom, sex injuries and how losing weight made his dick bigger. Things get a little steamy as they talk shower sex, vintage vagina, cheating and how and when to define a relationship. The Florida native joins Angela Yee, Stephanie Santiago, Gigi Maguire, and Lip Service's blogger Passport Cutty in this weeks episode.
